_sText:
I build this map for all gamers who wanna play a new map... a funny map with easy ways and with a abience like the summer in ur dreams :)

U can load this map up to all servers and hompages.

Don't changes anything on this map without my consent!

And now i wish u much fun with this map :)


I fixed many bugs

- for 64 Players now
- Ct's and T's are on the bombside B at the same time.
- you can't climb any roofs
- you can see the roof of the church from every point of the map
- i put a box between the two houses in the near of the bonbside B
- i fixed the prop fade distance
- there is a box in the near of the fountain, on the right side of the stairs
- i put a rock in the near of the church for more cover
- bot waypoints
